query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1) NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from answer AS a1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('es',
'mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('android',
'css',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'fa.functional-analysis',
'php')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
